Yervand Garginian is a 60-year-old bus driver from South Croydon in Melbourne . 
  He filmed himself cooking chicken on an open charcoal barbecue at a recent family gathering . 
  His daughter Elizabeth Garginian posted the video to Reddit and it has been viewed more than five million times . 
  In the video Mr Garginian dismisses the Australian-style barbecue of cooking 'oily' sausages . 
 